                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/1422: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lima</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-10-10T22:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 10, 1931—10 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>334. Reference my 331 [<hi rend="italic">333</hi>] of today’s date,<note n="94"
                        xml:id="d622fn94">Not printed.</note> Foreign Minister has just informed me
                    he is instructing Peruvian Ambassador Washington to vigorously cooperate in
                    every possible way with the Department towards settling Chaco situation. He
                    states that on occasion of first of recent clashes he instructed Peruvian
                    Ministers in La Paz and Asunción to work for harmony and in interest of November
                    meeting and noncreation [<hi rend="italic">nonaggression?</hi>] pact and that he
                    ascertained that Chilean Government would take the same line. He is tonight
                    telegraphing Peruvian diplomatic representatives in Brazil <pb facs="0877"
                        n="763" xml:id="pg_763"/> and the Argentine to assist the issue in every way
                    they can and is sending additional messages to the Peruvian diplomatic
                    representatives in Chile, Bolivia, and Paraguay. The Foreign Minister intends
                    Peruvian cooperation shall be complete.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dearing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
